|-\n| ''Scotland's Story''\n| [[Charles Edward Stewart|Prince Charles Edward Stewart]]\n| TV mini-series, small role\n|-\n| ''Louisiana''\n| Clarence Dandridge\n| TV mini-series, leading role\n|-\n| ''[[Oxbridge Blues]]''\n| Victor Geary \n| TV play, ep. \"Oxbridge Blues\", starring role\n|-\n| ''[[The Sun Also Rises (1984 film)|The Sun Also Rises]]''\n| Mike Campbell\n| TV movie, small role\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|  1985\n| ''Royal Night of 100 Stars''\n| Himself\n| Singing performance, \"[[You're Just in Love]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[A Month in the Country (play)|A Month in the Country]]''\n| Rakitin\n| TV movie, leading role\n|-\n| 1986\n| ''[[Car Trouble (film)|Car Trouble]]''\n| Gerald Spong\n| Feature film, leading role\n|-\n| 1987\n| ''[[Opera (film)|Opera]]''\n| Marco\n| Feature film, main cast\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 1988\n| ''[[Codename: Kyril]]''\n| Kyril\n| TV movie, title role\n|-\n| ''[[Troubles (novel)|Troubles]]''\n| Maj. Brendan Archer\n| TV movie, starring role\n|}\n\n==Major theatre credits==\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 90%;\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" background: #f9f9f9;\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Year\n! style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Title\n! style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Role\n! style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Director\n! style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Playwright\n! style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Theatre\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 1972 \n| ''[[Joseph and the Amazing Technicolor Dreamcoat#American and Young Vic performances|Bible One]]'', Part I: <br>''[[Wakefield Mystery Plays|The Genesis Mediaeval Mystery Plays:'' <br>''The Creation to Jacob]]''\n| Angels / Noah's son\n| [[Frank Dunlop (director)|Frank Dunlop]]\n| Frank Dunlop <br>(adapter)\n| [[Young Vic|Young Vic Theatre Company]] at the <br>[[Edinburgh International Festival]]<br>[[Young Vic Theatre]]<br>[[The Roundhouse]]\n|-\n| ''[[Joseph and the Amazing Technicolor Dreamcoat|Joseph and the Amazing <br>Technicolor Dreamcoat]]''\n| [[Gad (son 